(@p90, @p91, @p92, @p93, 15),
(@p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, 16),
(@p98, @p99, @p100, @p101, 17)) AS i ([AuthorId], [Date], [Name], [Price], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AuthorId], [Date], [Name], [Price])
VALUES (i.[AuthorId], i.[Date], i.[Name], i.[Price])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position;

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AuthorId], [Date], [Name], [Price])
VALUES (i.[AuthorId], i.[Date], i.[Name], i.[Price])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position;
